#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-kapplication; is an editor for Sieve scripts used for email filtering "
"on a mail server."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication; on e-posti serveris kirjade filtreerimiseks kasutatavate "
"Sieve Skriptide redaktor."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sieve"
msgstr "Sieve"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-kapplication; is an editor for <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Sieve_(mail_filtering_language)\">Sieve</ulink> scripts used for email "
"filtering on a mail server."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication; on e-posti serveris kirjade filtreerimiseks kasutatavate "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Sieve_(mail_filtering_language)\">Sieve</ulink> skriptide redaktor."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &i18n-kapplication;"
msgstr "&i18n-kapplication;i kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-kapplication; provides a &GUI; to perform these tasks:"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication;i graafiline kasutajaliides võimaldab ette võtta järgmist:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manage your Sieve servers"
msgstr "Hallata oma Sieve servereid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Upload, import and deactivate scripts, refresh the list with scripts"
msgstr ""
"Laadida üles, importida ja deaktiveerida skripte ning värskendada "
"skriptiloendit"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create and edit Sieve scripts"
msgstr "Luua ja muuta Sieve skripte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and share scripts"
msgstr "Importida ja jagada skripte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the script syntax, autogenerate and debug scripts"
msgstr ""
"Kontrollida skriptide süntaksit ning skripte automaatselt genereerida ja "
"siluda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-kapplication; can be used independent from Akonadi or &kmail;, you "
"only need a mail server with support for Sieve scripts."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication;it saab kasutada sõltumata Akonadist või &kmail;ist: vaja "
"läheb ainult e-posti serverit, mis toetab Sieve skripte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "In a &plasma-desktop; the passwords are stored in &kwallet5;"
msgstr "Plasma töölaua korral salvestab paroolid &kwallet5;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "First Start"
msgstr "Esimene käivitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the first start of &i18n-kapplication; the server configuration dialog is "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication;i esimesel käivitamisel ilmub nähtavale serveri "
"seadistamise dialoog."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Server Configuration</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Serveri seadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Server Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Serveri seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this dialog you can add, modify and remove your mails servers."
msgstr "Selles dialoogis saab e-posti servereid lisada, muuta ja eemaldada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Later you can use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add "
"Server</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or the configuration dialog for these "
"tasks."
msgstr ""
"Hiljem saab samade ülesannete tarbeks kasutada menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Lisa server</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> või seadistusdialoogi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the next start &i18n-kapplication; automatically fetches all available "
"scripts from the servers."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication;i järgmisel käivitamisel tõmmatakse serveritest "
"automaatselt kõik saadaolevad skriptid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Script Editing</title>"
msgstr "<title>Skripti muutmine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editor supports autocompletion and syntax highlighting."
msgstr "Redaktor toetab automaatset lõpetamist ja süntaksi esiletõstmist."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Script Editing</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skripti muutmine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Script Editing</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skripti muutmine</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Tools"
msgstr "Skriptitööriistad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actions in the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu enable you to check the "
"syntax of your scripts, autogenerate and debug scripts."
msgstr ""
"Menüü <guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu> kirjetega saab kontrollida oma skriptide "
"süntaksit ning neid automaatselt genereerida ja siluda."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Autogenerate scripts</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skriptide automaatne genereerimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Autogenerate scripts</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skriptide automaatne genereerimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Integrated Help</title>"
msgstr "<title>Lõimitud abi</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the integrated help support and click with the &RMB; on a "
"keyword of the Sieve language. Then the corresponding section of the "
"documentation is downloaded from the Internet and displayed in the "
"<guilabel>Help</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Soovi korral saab kasutada lõimitud abi ning klõpsata &HPNga; Sieve keele "
"võtmesõnal. Seejärel laaditakse internetist alla dokumentatsiooni vastav osa "
"ja näidatakse seda kaardil <guilabel>Abi</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Integrated Help</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Lõimitud abi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Integrated Help</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Lõimitud abi</phrase>"

